day 62 : Discount-20% program 

IN C :
# Input original price
original_price = float(input("Enter the original price of the product: "))

# Calculate discount (20% of the original price)
discount = original_price * 0.20

# Calculate final price after discount
final_price = original_price - discount

# Display the results
print(f"Original Price: ${original_price:.2f}")
print(f"Discount Amount (20%): ${discount:.2f}")
print(f"Final Price after discount: ${final_price:.2f}")

O/P :

Enter the original price of the product: 100
Original Price: $100.00
Discount Amount (20%): $20.00
Final Price after discount: $80.00

IN PYTHON :

# Input original price
original_price = float(input("Enter the original price of the product: "))

# Calculate discount (20% of the original price)
discount = original_price * 0.20

# Calculate final price after discount
final_price = original_price - discount

# Display the results
print(f"Original Price: ${original_price:.2f}")
print(f"Discount Amount (20%): ${discount:.2f}")
print(f"Final Price after discount: ${final_price:.2f}")

